%F A395465 Equals sqrt(3 + 2*sqrt(3))/6.
%F A395465 Equals f(3*theta) - f(theta), where theta = A395469, and f(x) = x/sin(x)^2 - cot(x)/4.
%F A395465 Minimal polynomial: 432*x^4 - 72*x^2 - 1.
